# Ansible Molecule Images for {{ item.display_name }}

This repository contains Ansible [Molecule](https://docs.ansible.com/projects/molecule/) images
for {{ item.display_name }}.

## Images

The images in this repository are based on [{{ item.pull_image }}]({{ source_url }})
and include `{{ init_system }}` and Python and the according package manager and libraries,
making them suitable for testing Ansible roles with [Molecule](https://docs.ansible.com/projects/molecule/).

## {{ item.display_name }} Versions

The repository provides images for the following {{ item.display_name }} variants:

