## Usage

To use these images in [Molecule](https://docs.ansible.com/projects/molecule/),
reference them in your `molecule.yml`.

### Molecule `docker` driver

To use the {{ item.display_name }} {{ example_tag }} image with the docker driver:

```yaml
platforms:
  - name: instance
    image: "{{ image_ref }}:{{ example_tag }}"
    privileged: true
```

### Molecule `podman` driver

To use the {{ item.display_name }} {{ example_tag }} image with the podman driver:

```yaml
platforms:
  - name: instance
    image: "docker.io/{{ image_ref }}:{{ example_tag }}"
```

This will start a container with {{ item.display_name }} {{ example_tag }} and `{{ init_system }}` as `pid 0`,
which you can then use for testing your Ansible roles.

